<title>
Front Suspension Fasteners Check
</title>
<ptxt>
Check bolts and nuts fastening suspension parts for tightness. Tighten loose fastener, if any, to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
For specified torque, refer to:
</ptxt>
